title: NEW TOWNHOME @ NEW LOWER PRICE - No Fees, Just $1000 Moves you in!
posting_body: ['Are you tire of paying an ever-increasing rent?', 'Give us a call today!!', 'show contact info', 'ext.', '300', 'You could own this amazing 3-Bed/2-Bath Home for only $2,109 per month.', 'With our help, the dream of homeownership is possible!', 'We have helped hundreds of people in the Seattle area get out of their apartment and into a brand new home of their own.', 'Learn how you can own this home in the gorgeous community of Gilman Walk by calling us today!', 'This stunning new townhome features an open entertaining area on the first floor with a spacious living room & dining area.', 'The kitchen is upgraded with quartz countertops, 42” staggered cabinets, & a full set of stainless steel Whirlpool® appliances.', 'Designer plank flooring, two-tone paint & recessed LED lighting create a beautiful backdrop for making memories with family & friends in this gorgeous home.', 'Upstairs, enjoy a private owner’s retreat with a dual-sink vanity & walk-in closet, plus two more bedrooms & a second full bathroom.', 'Additional designer upgrades in this home include comfort light switches, satin nickel door levers, Moen faucets, a programmable thermostat & 2” faux wood window blinds.', 'We can help YOU get into the home of your dreams with just $1000!', 'Call', 'show contact info', 'and mention extension', '300', 'for more details.', '*P & I. Price $469,900, 5.5% Fixed/5.541% APR, 20% Down, CONV 30 Year, OAC from third party lender.', 'Other fees such as taxes, insurance, and HOA are not included in the sample monthly payment amount.', ' Prices and rates are subject to change without notice.']
